	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Dec 22nd 3:20 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The item haste from the girdle will not stack with the sword. You can only have one haste due to item, spell or song at a time. You could have an item haste, a spell haste and a song haste at the same time, but not two from the same category. <br>&nbsp;<br>Banvaren Holybane<br>38 Paladin <br>Povar Server</td></tr>
